      "updated": 1700000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How it connects:\n\nCaddy (the reverse proxy) routes traffic based on URL path:\n  /prestecs/*  ->  App container (FastAPI + React)     = dynamic, with database and login\n  everything else  ->  Static files                    = Ariadna's HTML/CSS pages\n\nBoth live on the same domain, same server. One Caddy config ties them together.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "how-box",
      "originalText": "How it connects:\n\nCaddy (the reverse proxy) routes traffic based on URL path:\n  /prestecs/*  ->  App container (FastAPI + React)     = dynamic, with database and login\n  everything else  ->  Static files                    = Ariadna's HTML/CSS pages\n\nBoth live on the same domain, same server. One Caddy config ties them together.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
